OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784137703
OL,3,CLeale's Yard demolition to begin in
OL,4,CSeptember
OL,6,FThe demolition of buildings at Leale's
OL,7,FYard will begin in September,
OL,8,Faccording to the States of Guernsey.
OL,10,FThe President of the Policy and
OL,11,FResources Committee, Deputy Lindsay de
OL,12,FSausmarez, said in January that the
OL,13,Fsite would be clear before the end of
OL,14,F2026 and planning for demolition was
OL,15,Fapproved in June.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
