OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784137703
OL,3,CLeale's Yard demolition to begin in
OL,4,CSeptember
OL,6,FThe Government now says that September
OL,7,Fwill be the first of two demolition
OL,8,Fstages, with work expected to continue
OL,9,Finto spring 2027 to leave a "flat and
OL,10,Fsafe site that is ready for
OL,11,Fdevelopment".
OL,13,FThis will involve removing some parts,
OL,14,Fsuch as roof coverings and windows, by
OL,15,Fhand and working alongside ecologists
OL,16,Fso that birds and bats can leave
OL,17,Fnaturally.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784137703
OL,3,CLeale's Yard demolition to begin in
OL,4,CSeptember
OL,6,FMaterials will be sorted and kept
OL,7,Fwhere possible for reuse on future
OL,8,Fprojects, with the building demolished
OL,9,Ffrom the top down to try and prevent
OL,10,Fexcessive dust.
OL,12,FEventually, this will lead to the
OL,13,Fremoval of any contaminated soil and
OL,14,Futilities will be capped.
OL,16,FDeputy Yvonne Burford, Vice-President
OL,17,Fof the Policy and Resources Committee,
OL,18,Fexplains in a statement that
OL,19,F"significant progress has been made in
OL,20,Fthe background to get us to where we
OL,21,Fare today".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784137703
OL,3,CLeale's Yard demolition to begin in
OL,4,CSeptember
OL,6,FShe adds: "We are ensuring that the
OL,7,Fdemolition process is done in such a
OL,8,Fway that it minimises noise, dust and
OL,9,Fgeneral disturbance to residents and
OL,10,Fbusinesses in the area, and that it is
OL,11,Fsympathetic to wildlife."
OL,13,FThe Guernsey Retail Group (GRG) say
OL,14,Fthey are "pleased to hear that
OL,15,Fdemolition work will finally begin".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784137703
OL,3,CLeale's Yard demolition to begin in
OL,4,CSeptember
OL,6,FThey add: "The lack of progress in
OL,7,Fthis area has left parts of the Bridge
OL,8,Flooking tired and neglected and has
OL,9,Fsometimes detracted from the positive
OL,10,Fwork done by the variety of retailers
OL,11,Fin the area.
OL,13,F"The GRG would also like to see this
OL,14,Fdevelopment form part of a wider
OL,15,Fprogramme of regeneration around St
OL,16,FSampson's Harbour and The Bridge."
OL,18,FSo, how did we get here?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784137703
OL,3,CLeale's Yard demolition to begin in
OL,4,CSeptember
OL,6,FWell, the Channel Islands Co-op bought
OL,7,Fthe site in the 1990s and it has been
OL,8,Fstanding empty and earmarked for
OL,9,Fdevelopment for the last 30 years.
OL,11,FThe States of Guernsey then purchased
OL,12,Fmost of it last July for #4.5 million
OL,13,Fand has finally come up with plans to
OL,14,Fclear the site in September.
OL,16,FIt has been an eyesore for decades and
OL,17,Fa real blight on St Sampson. The
OL,18,Foutbuildings are also dangerous and
OL,19,Fsecurity fences don't always keep
OL,20,Fpeople out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784137703
OL,3,CLeale's Yard demolition to begin in
OL,4,CSeptember
OL,6,FWith the need for a revamp on the
OL,7,FBridge and a wider shortage of
OL,8,Fhousing, the potential to develop the
OL,9,Fsite has always been welcomed by those
OL,10,Fliving and working in the north of the
OL,11,Fisland.
OL,13,FThe question is, will it live up to
OL,14,Fits potential?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
